reviews.text: This restaurant has been around for years and still it is going strong. I called three days in advance to make a reservation for a Saturday night. I called 4 hours prior to the reservation to add one more guest and that was fine. Even though we were 5, we had a spacious table for 6 reserved and awaiting our arrival. The food was delicious as usual but some menu items we wanted were unavailable. If you are sensitive to spice, make sure to ask for 'less spice' to bring itl down to 'foreigner-spicy' levels.
The food tasted amazing as it was cooked by authentic, native Thai chefs. I felt like I was in Thailand with the setting, music, and accomodous staff. I loved my dinner and I will surely come back!
So well priced for a lunch in Central. Amazing deal for decent food
The best Tom Yum soup (vegetarian) that I had so far! We all found our foods delicious and really recommend it! Also enough vegetarian options

Authentic Thai food with big portion 😂
Yummy!

Pad thai午餐$72，非常甜沒附檸檬，海鮮有腥味是小蛤蜊+小章魚碎碎的這樣。很甜的醬沒有炒的香氣，非～～～常一般。
青咖哩豬排飯$68 非～～～常普通
甜點是椰奶芋頭紫米是正常好吃的
除了在中環區經濟實惠服務一般ok以外
可能不會再來....有四顆星評價應該是給晚餐的吧

덩라우 벽화쪽에서 시장쪽 언덕으로 내려가는길 우측에 있는 음식점. 
모닝글로리의 적당하게 익힘정도
닭고기 퐛타이 2명이 먹기에 양과 질 모두 훌륭.
디저트는 코코넛을 먹고싶었지만 망고만 있었다.
망고는 그냥 그랬다.
모닝글로리와 퐛타이는 훌륭했다
직원 또한 친절했다.
가격도 총 235홍딸
